{"tid":1154352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"持貨500萬元的公屋富戶","createTime":"2019-05-14T08:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T09:55:31.000Z","uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9de50aca5ac121c54e3232b90db03aaec3e5b004","tid":1154352,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:43:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190513/59587344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190513%2F59587344&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ4GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=7b4a4ad4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190513%2F59587344&h=c33d008b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190513/59587344</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》亦走訪九龍及新界多個持有領展的公屋戶，其中元洲邨、寶達邨及柴灣邨皆為租住單位，當中不乏持貨市值近500萬元的大戶，有機會因基金升值，超逾現行公屋資產淨值成為「公屋富戶」。有租戶向記者指，子女用他們的名義購入領展，故對基金走勢、前景等都不太清楚。<br />\n<br />\n政府應查明各股票戶口持有人是否居於公屋單位<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJDE0hh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJDE0hh.jpg&h=de02b556&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1774fc9c9ed3447b2d68c6af9bec65880e45e95","tid":1154352,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xS9EfSc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxS9EfSc.png&h=a2885dee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb4bd41d3312ff68692ddcc6981b29b2f8219eed","tid":1154352,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:48:28.000Z","msg":"過左60歲咪無野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c4a3e94577ae874b09a81fbd1e3e7971ea520d","tid":1154352,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:49:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除